data.oai_dc:dc: This data file contains the data used to determine the extrapolated number of seeds dispersed by both species of tamarins (Saguinus nigrifrons and Saguinus fuscicollis), corresponding to the quantity component of seed dispersal effectiveness (SDE). These data were used to build the SDE landscape.
